{"tid":792744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安泰邪邨】秀茂坪安泰邨22歲仔墮樓　跌落籃球場死亡","createTime":"2018-08-24T18:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T00:00:33.000Z","uid":50162,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea087115db30218c8817c2679eb6c719f138951","tid":792744,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:49:35.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪安泰邨一名男子從高處墮下死亡，今日(22日)晚上9時46分，警方接獲一名姓周(46歲)女子報案，指其姓蔡22歲兒子從和泰樓高處墮下。警員及救護員隨即趕赴現場，發現蔡倒臥和泰樓對出一個籃球場，毫無氣息，救護員初步驗驗後證實事主死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警員以帳篷覆蓋死者遺體，而死者的親友亦趕至認屍，不禁悲從中來。據悉，死者生前受感情問題困擾，墮樓前曾向親友發短訊，警方正作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/photo/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180823055738\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180822%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180823055738&h=cc1bc55f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子(黃圈示)高處墮下跌落籃球場身亡，警方到場調查。(讀者提供/梁裔楠攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/photo/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180823055738\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180822%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180823055738&h=94056c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子(黃圈示)高處墮下當場不治。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/photo/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180823055738\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180822%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180823055738&h=15200950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在場調查。(梁裔楠攝)<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180822%2Fbkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001.html&d=M8i2fWUDF8sHz5hPwwaZZ57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=599dd459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n＃安泰邪邨 ＃前石礦場 ＃死亡勝地 ＃每月送命"},{"pid":"4a033a95375113ae0687a1ff1f0a9de3afb500da","tid":792744,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T19:01:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97c7a176e2377eca7dbe02ca6f6fa1b5f508d1f0","tid":792744,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T19:47:00.000Z","msg":"睇怕佢老母岩岩同佢嘈完黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733a662a8f7fafdee75421bcaf9ba183a5765740","tid":792744,"uid":47485,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T19:52:19.000Z","msg":"嘩 跳到咁撚遠<br />\n一個唔好彩 責親人就仆街了"},{"pid":"504264d29a05cf1ec834528679d9f37ae209ea01","tid":792744,"uid":36970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T20:00:27.000Z","msg":"其實都幾高難度"},{"pid":"0365f2087f6f9798c9d4240a1904f1919fd66dd8","tid":792744,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"733a662a8f7fafdee75421bcaf9ba183a5765740","tid":792744,"uid":47485,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T19:52:19.000Z","msg":"嘩 跳到咁撚遠<br />\n一個唔好彩 責親人就仆街了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T18:55:23.000Z","msg":"其實唔遠，因為個籃球場就係正樓下，非常接近民居！"},{"pid":"e290b6b176b4813505fd701b6c9dbd96c571ffef","tid":792744,"uid":118502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T18:58:08.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始跳樓已經習已為常"},{"pid":"8cff63e13b911183f46973301c027407e13f65b1","tid":792744,"uid":72226,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a033a95375113ae0687a1ff1f0a9de3afb500da","tid":792744,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"re